<p id="comment-truncated-4983-1674285249" class="comment">
Bittersweet Legacy is a beautiful anthology of works by artists and writers haunted (as the world is) by the Holocaust. My work was included, Cynthia Brody was the tireless editor and contributor. It became an exhibition at the Triton Museum, Santa...
</p>
<p id="comment-full-4983-1674285249" class="comment" style="display: none">
Bittersweet Legacy is a beautiful anthology of works by artists and writers haunted (as the world is) by the Holocaust. My work was included, Cynthia Brody was the tireless editor and contributor. It became an exhibition at the Triton Museum, Santa Clara, California.
</p>
